WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:02.880
Niko vam nikad neće platiti
koliko vrijedite.

00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:08.216
Nikad vam niko neće platiti


00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:09.440
onoliko koliko vrijedite.

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:13.776
Platit će vam samo

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:15.431
onoliko koliko misle da vrijedite.

00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:18.080
A vi kontrolišete šta oni misle,

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:20.800
ne ovako,

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:22.856
iako bi to bilo super.

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:24.496
(Smijeh)

00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:25.800
To bi stvarno bilo super.

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:28.640
Umjesto toga, ovako:

00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:34.136
ključno je da jasno definišete
i saopštite vašu vrijednost